executionArgs.additionalInstruction: Use 'http://127.0.0.1:8000' as the BASE_URL. Ensure 'allow_redirects=False' is used when verifying 302 redirects for unauthenticated access. For the logout test (TC006), if you are doing a POST request, note that it requires a CSRF token in Django. If you cannot easily obtain a CSRF token, focus on the GET accessibility or simple redirection logic.
